{"tid":1476622,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有市民帶同工具到港鐵葵芳站清潔","createTime":"2019-08-16T01:04:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T02:29:26.000Z","uid":51271,"like":42,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"be475e6b598e75f900443ae45b31fb2cfff62843","tid":1476622,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T01:04:09.000Z","msg":"有市民響應網上呼籲，自發到港鐵葵芳站清潔。<br />\n<br />\n其中居住在油麻地的陳先生，早上特意請假半天，帶同清潔工具到葵芳站內清潔牆身等地方，他表示希望盡力幫助社區。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，警方在記者會上強調催淚彈對人體無害，但他擔心可能之後會出現問題，建議警方若覺得沒問題可以落區親身感受，而不是只相信生產商說明。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1474982_1_L_20190816084011.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1474982_1_L_20190816084011.jpg&h=7b6a368a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ca1e308bb9045c2bc2395fd5a33ca52bc7445908","tid":1476622,"uid":34777,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T01:04:43.000Z","msg":"巴打好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1da362db0bb588c92a9f4137a614bcefda317f38","tid":1476622,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T01:06:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1205cd721fb6d01997221707b11f6cb3a380a63","tid":1476622,"uid":24707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T01:09:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67527e18c2d6afc036a7739138f817af012666f5","tid":1476622,"uid":176657,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T01:13:09.000Z","msg":"巴打好男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick